  <title>接近开关 LS1319（低液位检测）</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">接近开关 LS1319（低液位检测）</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;">接近开关 LS1319（低液位检测）安装在液位计上。当切削液液位下降到下限液位以下时，接近开关会检测到狗并按以下顺序触发警报。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;">以下尺寸适用于不使用冷却液的机床。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">警报触发顺序</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">切削液液位下降，浮球和阀狗下降到下限液位以下。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;<text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">¯</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">接近开关 LS1319 检测狗（检测切削液液位低）。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;<text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">¯</text> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">机床控制装置触发 EX1525 号警报</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
